Test Coverage

The following tests should be covered in this application:

1.  Unit tests for the "calculate_factorial(n)" function, to make sure that the function is calculating
    the factorial of the entered number.

2.  Integration tests for the application to make sure that the endpoints return thr correct responses for different
    input cases.

3.  End-to-end testing with selenium. This is to test the application as whole and from a perspective of a user.

4.  Load testing, this is to make sure that the application can handle large traffic, without slowing down or crashing.


